WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.400 --> 00:00:02.589
Well, good evening, ladies and gentlemen.

00:00:02.589 --> 00:00:05.786
And to some of you, good morning, family.

00:00:05.786 --> 00:00:06.971
Praise the Lord.

00:00:06.971 --> 00:00:08.912
Thank you for joining me again tonight.

00:00:08.912 --> 00:00:12.285
I really appreciate y'all showing up every time and praying.

00:00:12.285 --> 00:00:13.1000
It means a lot to me.

00:00:14.288 --> 00:00:15.872
We have work to do.

00:00:15.872 --> 00:00:37.840
But as we see some of the news today, there was an earthquake in California today, my son was telling me, and I don't know if it was too big of one, but it's an earthquake and it was on the larger scale as you all can see maybe by this map.

00:00:37.840 --> 00:01:01.659
And so I thought that was kind of interesting that it happened today as we see another vote going for a two-state solution on a very significant day, the eve of Rosh Hashanah.

00:01:01.659 --> 00:01:18.320
England made a very strong stance for a two-state solution today, from what I understand, and the only nations that sided with Israel were, I think my wife told me, three.

00:01:18.320 --> 00:01:28.571
It was a pretty clear stance, and the ones that were undecided, the number went down to like less than five or something.

00:01:29.165 --> 00:01:30.912
The numbers were ridiculous.

00:01:30.912 --> 00:01:32.576
I couldn't believe it.

00:01:32.576 --> 00:01:35.296
Actually, Australia went with it.

00:01:35.984 --> 00:01:37.360
Basically, everybody.

00:01:37.640 --> 00:01:45.973
The United States is the lone ranger out here with, I think, three other nations, but they took the vote again today.

00:01:45.973 --> 00:01:57.584
From what I understood, I was actually shocked by the level of support that voted for a two-state solution.

00:01:57.584 --> 00:02:05.391
I told my wife, I said, 'Wow, you know, okay.

00:02:05.391 --> 00:02:28.400
' But just like the Lord told us that as we enter into tomorrow, we would see the sheep and the goat nations and that a line would be drawn in the sand, and we would see the ones that will bless and the ones that will curse.

00:02:28.400 --> 00:02:35.200
And we're seeing that unfold in front of our faces at an alarming rate.

00:02:35.200 --> 00:02:37.360
So, do you have that article?

00:02:37.360 --> 00:02:40.800
Do you have that thing from your mama?

00:02:40.800 --> 00:02:41.813
I don't think so.

00:02:41.813 --> 00:02:46.000
I've written Australia, Canada, and Portugal recognize a Palestinian state.

00:02:46.000 --> 00:02:52.089
Yeah, son, but Mom had that chart, and it had each actual vote and who voted with what.

00:02:52.089 --> 00:02:54.330
But if you can't find it, that's fine.

00:02:54.879 --> 00:02:55.493
She's in there.

00:02:55.493 --> 00:02:58.280
You just have to get it from her phone.

00:02:58.280 --> 00:03:01.440
But she was telling me all that.

00:03:01.440 --> 00:03:09.360
But I'll go over some of the things that we were shown, what I was shown in prayer last night.

00:03:09.640 --> 00:03:22.773
I thought the visions last night, when the Lord was showing us about the AI and the new industrial revolution that was being displayed before me, were interesting.

00:03:23.146 --> 00:03:29.519
Every single time he shows me something, it's at a different angle.

00:03:29.519 --> 00:03:33.405
It adds to the puzzle, but it's at a different angle.

00:03:33.405 --> 00:03:38.240
And I think that is, you know, to me, I just go, 'Lord, you're so awesome.

00:03:38.240 --> 00:03:42.088
' The natural man perceiveth not the things of God.

00:03:42.088 --> 00:03:44.959
You have to get it out of the spirit.

00:03:44.959 --> 00:03:51.920
But whenever you're getting it and he's downloading things to you like he did to me last night, ladies and gentlemen, it was beautiful.

00:03:51.920 --> 00:04:02.319
The colors and the visions when the Lord is speaking to me are so full of life.

00:04:02.319 --> 00:04:10.239
You just see the colors and everything, and I try to grasp them as I'm on a live stream.

00:04:10.239 --> 00:04:31.1000
When I'm in my private time and we pray, I have time to focus on each one, and I pause and I just reflect, and I'm able to really just soak in and memorize that moment in my spirit and be able to tell my wife and my children what the Lord is showing us.

00:04:31.1000 --> 00:04:41.931
And when it's a live stream, because it's so public, I don't have that opportunity a lot of times because he doesn't let me park there.

00:04:41.931 --> 00:04:43.371
That's why he tells me, 'Keep going.

00:04:43.371 --> 00:04:43.783
Keep going.

00:04:43.783 --> 00:04:47.220
' Because I'm just telling you what I'm hearing.

00:04:47.220 --> 00:04:57.520
But I like to stop and soak in the moment, everything that I'm seeing, because the visions are beautiful to me.

00:04:57.520 --> 00:04:59.759
They're precious.

00:05:00.283 --> 00:05:12.720
I never just bypass them, but for the sake of time and what he's trying to do on these streams with you all is to warn you of what's coming.

00:05:12.720 --> 00:05:25.840
And as we go into the 23rd in the next couple of hours here and we pray into the 23rd because I believe, you know, I believe Israel is already into the 23rd for sure by a long shot.

00:05:25.840 --> 00:05:39.600
But, you know, I'm not attacking anybody's faith of where they're believing for the 23rd and the 24th that the rapture of the church would take place.

00:05:39.600 --> 00:05:42.114
I pray you're all right.

00:05:42.114 --> 00:05:43.862
You know, that'd be awesome.

00:05:43.862 --> 00:05:50.279
But I believe that there'll be many of you that are disappointed in the next 48 hours.

00:05:50.279 --> 00:05:55.039
And I don't want you to be down.

00:05:55.039 --> 00:06:05.013
I don't want you to lose faith or lose heart in being weary in well-doing as you are still here.

00:06:05.013 --> 00:06:09.280
And you'll probably be mad at me, saying, 'Brad, I don't want to hear this,' and wanting to click off.

00:06:09.280 --> 00:06:12.400
I'm just being real with you.

00:06:15.520 --> 00:06:18.144
I just want to prepare you that we still have some work to do.

00:06:24.640 --> 00:06:25.200
I knew it, and I've tried to warn you as we're still here.

00:06:30.899 --> 00:06:31.159
And wouldn't it be wonderful if he took us right now?

00:06:52.070 --> 00:06:52.280
But I know what he's showed me.

00:06:52.280 --> 00:07:08.656
I know what I'm called to tell you to pray and that there's going to be a great shaking to awaken the church, and that the church isn't ready.

00:07:21.039 --> 00:07:21.279
The people aren't ready.

00:07:21.279 --> 00:07:27.343
They're asleep; the vast majority of the church is asleep.

00:07:27.343 --> 00:07:41.794
Yeah, we have a group of people, but you have, you know, even 100,000 people yesterday in a service with, you know, a couple million people watching on a live stream.

00:07:49.680 --> 00:07:51.080
And a lot of people called that a revival.

00:08:03.170 --> 00:08:03.440
And if that's a revival, I'm very disappointed.

00:08:03.440 --> 00:08:06.840
There are over 8 billion people on this earth.

00:08:08.240 --> 00:08:10.759
And it could be the beginning of revival.

00:08:18.079 --> 00:08:18.319
I could see maybe just the first drops of rain falling.

00:08:18.319 --> 00:08:25.730
But what is it going to take to get the people who are not even...

00:08:25.730 --> 00:08:33.989
I watched the interview from one of the CNN reporters, and he was just belligerent in what he was saying against the church and the radical evangelicals.

00:08:33.989 --> 00:08:41.251
The things that he was saying were so rude against the church, so blasphemous.

00:08:41.251 --> 00:08:44.937
But he said, 'This is my right of free speech.

00:08:44.937 --> 00:08:50.160
' And the things he was saying were poison.

00:08:53.960 --> 00:08:54.220
And I watched it, and I was like, 'Wow.

00:08:54.220 --> 00:08:58.663
' 'This is my truth' is what he kept saying.

00:08:58.663 --> 00:08:59.417
'This is my truth.

00:08:59.417 --> 00:09:00.811
This is my reality.

00:09:00.811 --> 00:09:06.754
' And I thought, 'Well, sir, your reality and your truth—you're a toxic, evil individual.

00:09:06.754 --> 00:09:11.850
' And I listened to it, and it was hard to swallow.

00:09:21.703 --> 00:09:22.034
It was very...

00:09:35.560 --> 00:09:35.920
I told Diana—we were watching—I said, 'This makes me boil inside.

00:09:50.400 --> 00:09:50.800
This makes me boil inside.

00:09:50.800 --> 00:09:57.013
' And I was like, 'You want to play some of it, show the worship?

00:09:57.013 --> 00:09:59.271
' There was like two hours.

00:09:59.271 --> 00:10:00.860
Let's listen to Don Lemon.

00:10:00.860 --> 00:10:01.240
Okay.

00:10:01.240 --> 00:10:03.289
Didn't know if it said Demon or Lemon.

00:10:14.891 --> 00:10:15.749
Go ahead, Don.

00:10:30.000 --> 00:10:30.434
And here is where we have to tell the truth here.

00:10:34.560 --> 00:10:35.067
Okay, so here's the truth.

00:10:35.067 --> 00:10:38.080
Don's going to break it down.

00:10:38.080 --> 00:10:39.039
Here's the media.

00:10:39.039 --> 00:10:43.383
Also, did you guys know people on the left, they don't know what just happened?

00:10:43.383 --> 00:10:50.560
If you are in your little sandbox echo chamber of the left, you don't even know if that guy was Republican, Democrat, nothing.

00:10:50.560 --> 00:10:55.211
There was a poll taken and like 10% actually knew.

00:10:55.211 --> 00:10:59.680
Like, yeah, it was just this deranged Republican.

00:11:06.368 --> 00:11:06.576
What we saw in that arena was not simply faith finding public expression.

00:11:06.576 --> 00:11:07.616
Yeah, it really was.

00:11:08.800 --> 00:11:12.800
When his wife got up there and said, 'I'm going to start crying now,' and said, 'I forgive him.

00:11:12.800 --> 00:11:14.937
' Bring the tissue boxes.

00:11:14.937 --> 00:11:20.343
I will have to say that is one thing...

00:11:20.343 --> 00:11:22.782
you have him...

00:11:29.262 --> 00:11:29.493
just separates.

00:11:53.920 --> 00:11:54.399
That was a display of the truth.

00:11:54.399 --> 00:11:56.301
'That is my truth.

00:11:56.301 --> 00:11:57.920
This is my freedom of expression.

00:11:57.920 --> 00:12:03.760
This is my First Amendment right to be able to tell you the truth from my point of view.

00:12:03.760 --> 00:12:06.036
Not just from my point of view.

00:12:14.079 --> 00:12:14.470
This is what it is.

00:12:14.470 --> 00:12:21.560
' Talk some more, Don, so we could see who you are.

00:12:21.560 --> 00:12:26.251
Oh, and the orange guy got skipped, honey.

00:12:27.813 --> 00:12:29.223
The truth is Jesus says, 'By their fruit, you'll know.

00:12:29.223 --> 00:12:30.936
' Go ahead, Don.

00:12:30.936 --> 00:12:35.139
We'll take a look at your fruit.

00:12:35.139 --> 00:12:36.139
'...

00:12:36.139 --> 00:12:40.411
was religious nationalism on full display.

00:12:40.411 --> 00:12:44.100
That is the truth.

00:12:44.100 --> 00:12:46.200
That is my truth.

00:13:07.880 --> 00:13:08.080
This is my freedom of expression.

00:13:08.080 --> 00:13:08.674
This is...

00:13:08.674 --> 00:13:09.645
' So, religious nationalism.

00:13:10.289 --> 00:13:10.440
And so as you...

00:13:10.440 --> 00:13:11.040
Am I muted?

00:13:11.040 --> 00:13:11.497
Yeah.

00:13:11.497 --> 00:13:11.954
Huh?

00:13:11.954 --> 00:13:12.411
No.

00:13:12.411 --> 00:13:13.146
No, you're not.

00:13:13.146 --> 00:13:13.484
Okay.

00:13:13.484 --> 00:13:14.160
So, religious nationalism.

00:13:23.066 --> 00:13:23.493
Some of the things that the far left, these people are saying, are very toxic.

00:13:36.552 --> 00:13:36.864
So, you listen to it and that's his truth, you know, and he's entitled to his truth.

00:13:38.736 --> 00:13:50.015
And I'm not trying to rile everybody up, but I'm trying to tell you the great deception that is upon the world.

00:13:51.519 --> 00:14:00.880
And these are the people that we're trying to reach for Jesus right now.

00:14:26.240 --> 00:14:26.684
And I know there's a lot of people that are going to probably be disappointed tomorrow, is what I just know inside of what I'm hearing when I'm praying today.

00:14:26.684 --> 00:14:56.760
There's going to be a lot of people that are going to be ready to give up tomorrow because you were so focused on the rapture of the church happening tomorrow, that it's going to be one of those—do not go into a slumber, a place of depression, and just be ready to give up and let go of the rope because you're weary and well-doing.

00:14:58.256 --> 00:14:59.600
Don't become weary and well-doing.

00:14:59.600 --> 00:15:01.279
Occupy until he comes.

00:15:01.279 --> 00:15:02.959
Occupy until he comes.

00:15:02.959 --> 00:15:03.967
Be vigilant.

00:15:03.967 --> 00:15:15.919
Be aggressive about our faith of telling people that he's still coming, even if not in what you believed in your time frame as we go into tomorrow.

00:15:15.919 --> 00:15:35.519
If we come to that road—and I'm telling you, I believe we will—but if you were so strong about it, and I know there's a lot of people that got so angry at me, but I've tried to warn you.

00:15:35.519 --> 00:15:39.484
This is where I believe we are in the next 40 to 48 hours.

00:15:39.484 --> 00:15:41.707
Don't give up on everything.

00:15:41.707 --> 00:15:43.040
Keep standing.

00:15:43.040 --> 00:15:46.960
Have that backbone like a crowbar.

00:15:46.960 --> 00:15:53.510
Even if you don't see the results of what you thought you were going to see, don't give up.

00:15:53.510 --> 00:15:57.508
Have that bulldog on a bone.

00:15:57.508 --> 00:16:06.520
I'm fighting for what I believe: that Jesus Christ is coming, and he's coming back for me.

00:16:06.520 --> 00:16:09.796
He's coming back for the glorious church.

00:16:09.796 --> 00:16:22.573
But right now, I believe we're seeing the first fruits, the first little stuff here of the beginning of something major about to happen.

00:16:23.813 --> 00:17:01.310
I told the Lord when I was in my prayer time this afternoon, I was just interceding and I was praying for the church and the state of the church because I know there's a lot of you that are very upset about things, and with all the things that are going on, and some of the people that I have personally talked to over the phone praying for certain things, and visions that I have seen, wanting more to the vision.

00:17:12.479 --> 00:17:12.719
"God, show me more so I can help.

00:17:12.719 --> 00:17:15.051
Show me more.

00:17:19.768 --> 00:17:20.043
" And he said, "Go back to the main thing.

00:17:43.520 --> 00:17:44.080
You never sought me for a vision.

00:17:44.080 --> 00:17:47.184
You sought me for relationship.

00:17:50.212 --> 00:17:50.506
And in relationship, the vision is shown.

00:17:50.506 --> 00:17:56.000
" I've never sought him for healing gifts like that, or visions, or any kind of gifting.

00:17:56.000 --> 00:18:10.266
Everything has always been purely out of just knowing that I've had learning problems, wasn't really able to do anything.

00:18:10.266 --> 00:18:19.909
I've always been a man that has just been desperate for him.

00:18:19.919 --> 00:18:44.480
And in my desperation for him has been a byproduct of a relationship of just seeking him with all my heart, because I was not ever able to pay my bills because I wasn't able to make a lot of money because I wasn't very smart.

00:18:48.320 --> 00:18:54.423
And I said, "Father, I can't provide for this beautiful wife that I have, or these beautiful children that you've given me.

00:18:59.669 --> 00:18:59.919
And I don't like living on food stamps.

00:19:14.720 --> 00:19:15.280
I don't like living in a shotgun house in the roughest neighborhood in where I'm at.

00:19:37.840 --> 00:19:38.500
But I know that if I seek you, I'll find you, and you're going to help me with my intellect to make me something more.

00:19:38.500 --> 00:19:46.960
" And in that, I lost myself in him.

00:20:42.559 --> 00:20:43.405
And I realized no matter how much I had around me, it never made me happy other than having a relationship with him.

00:20:43.405 --> 00:20:47.999
So that's where it all developed.

00:20:47.999 --> 00:20:57.160
It came out of desperation because I didn't know how to provide for my family.

00:21:34.159 --> 00:21:34.525
But then everything else became so it didn't matter anymore.

00:21:35.622 --> 00:22:03.584
I didn't care how much money I had in the bank because every day when I got home from work, I spent hours in prayer at my washing machine, doing laundry, helping my wife out.

00:22:03.584 --> 00:22:12.000
I'd sit in there and just pray and take care of my puppies, and I'd listen, and I'd be still, and I'd worship.

00:22:21.830 --> 00:22:22.180
And that's where it all developed from: a place of real desperation.

00:22:22.530 --> 00:22:29.909
And as I developed and the more I became acquainted and the more I became friends with the Father, he would come and visit.

00:22:30.830 --> 00:22:44.720
And I'm talking tangible to the point where I've had one face-to-face, flesh-to-flesh talking to him, and I thought I was going to die.

00:22:44.720 --> 00:22:46.824
Everything else has been visions.

00:23:07.648 --> 00:23:07.904
But my first physical encounter, I can tell you I thought I was going to die.

00:23:07.904 --> 00:23:10.440
My human body could not take it.

00:23:10.440 --> 00:23:32.679
It was so overwhelming, the visitation that I had, that even my wife when she came into the room, she thought I was dying because it scared her so bad.

00:23:32.679 --> 00:23:38.760
She felt the presence of the Lord.

00:23:38.760 --> 00:23:49.999
It scared her so bad in the natural that she started screaming.

00:23:49.999 --> 00:23:53.977
She said, "Oh my God, are you going?

00:23:53.977 --> 00:23:57.494
Is he taking you?

00:23:57.494 --> 00:24:09.830
" I said, "Jesus is here, and I see him.

00:24:23.040 --> 00:24:23.440
" And she says, "I can't see him, but I can feel him.

00:24:23.440 --> 00:24:25.211
Please don't take my husband.

00:24:25.211 --> 00:24:28.900
" She thought I was dying.

00:24:31.600 --> 00:24:34.651
I was in a pile of tears and absolute fear of God.

00:24:48.389 --> 00:24:56.991
The only thing I can tell you was it was so tangible that all I could do was just be on my face, and I was trying to just reach up and look at him because it was all I could do with the tangible presence of God in my house.

00:24:56.991 --> 00:25:06.440
Where it happened, it left a crack in the floor.

00:25:06.440 --> 00:25:11.072
And even still, as we left that house, I took pictures of that crack in the floor.

00:25:11.648 --> 00:25:25.420
And I used to tell my kids, I said, "That crack in the floor is where Jesus stood, and it left a portal in my home.

00:25:25.420 --> 00:25:46.100
" I cannot tell you how, but that portal, every time I went there and I prayed in that area, I could feel the presence of God tangibly on me.

00:26:06.960 --> 00:26:07.200
And if I had hard times, I'd just go stand in that spot.

00:26:07.200 --> 00:26:16.680
But I didn't tell anybody else about it because you get weirdness, you know, like a Mary, Mother, painted figure on the wall, and people want to come and have a shrine.

00:26:16.680 --> 00:26:25.440
No, it was something private between me and my wife and my kids.

00:26:37.699 --> 00:26:37.1000
But that crack in that floor, it showed up after.

00:26:44.183 --> 00:26:44.526
And I kid you not, I'll never forget that experience ever.

00:26:44.526 --> 00:26:46.240
Neither will my wife.

00:26:46.240 --> 00:26:54.720
You know, when you have an experience with Jesus, it will change you.

00:26:54.720 --> 00:27:01.503
And yeah, your flesh, you go back, you can sin, you do things because we're just human.

00:27:14.720 --> 00:27:15.029
But once you taste his glory, once you taste authentic, you'll never be the same.

00:27:15.029 --> 00:27:16.880
It does something to you.

00:27:16.880 --> 00:27:21.458
It does something to you.

00:27:21.458 --> 00:27:27.520
When you truly see his face, it does something to you.

00:27:27.520 --> 00:27:29.698
It makes you radical.

00:27:41.448 --> 00:27:41.617
I know the disciples, they got to spend those three years or so with him, and it made them radical.

00:27:57.919 --> 00:27:58.607
I can't imagine waking up every morning and having him tangibly there, Jesus Christ alive in the flesh.

00:27:58.607 --> 00:28:05.915
I had just about a five-minute encounter, if that.

00:28:05.915 --> 00:28:11.279
That one moment changed me forever.

00:28:11.279 --> 00:28:18.720
I have a lot of visions, y'all.

00:28:36.320 --> 00:28:36.620
And it's developed out of a relationship, even with what I'm telling you about raising dogs from the dead and having manifestations of even the devil.

00:28:36.620 --> 00:28:43.235
But that impartation that I got that day, my human vocabulary, even telling you right now, can't even do it justice.

00:28:48.676 --> 00:28:49.058
And it's changed my wife and I.

00:28:59.748 --> 00:29:00.102
It's changed us.

00:29:00.102 --> 00:29:06.133
But I tell you all that to say, I know more.

00:29:06.133 --> 00:29:19.851
I know when he comes and visits me, and he tells me there's more to be done.

00:29:19.851 --> 00:29:32.773
I know more about what—I know it's like I say, I go more by what he doesn't say than what he does.

00:29:32.773 --> 00:29:36.720
Do you know what I'm saying?

00:29:36.720 --> 00:30:05.835
Because we talk that much during the day and things, and he tells me, "Brandon, you have this to do, you have this planned out, and I have given you a three-year window to bring forth my people and tell them that I'm coming.

00:30:05.835 --> 00:30:08.231
" Yes, sir.

00:30:17.181 --> 00:30:23.400
And the more I develop in the relationship, the relationship is no longer like a child talking to his father; it's more of an adult child.

00:30:23.400 --> 00:30:25.699
It's different instructions now.

00:30:25.699 --> 00:30:28.159
It's more like a commander-in-chief, like a boss.

00:30:28.159 --> 00:30:39.960
Some days are intimate like they used to be, but more, it's more like a commander-in-chief talking to an employee.

00:30:47.904 --> 00:30:48.168
And I don't say that disrespectfully.

00:30:48.168 --> 00:30:52.490
It's different the way he speaks.

00:30:52.490 --> 00:30:57.039
And I know it's business.

00:30:57.039 --> 00:31:02.789
He has what he wants and he will get what he wants.

00:31:30.062 --> 00:31:30.284
He is God.

